window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A luxurious island. A mysterious invitation. A deadly secret</p> <p>When amateur sleuth Charlotte \"Charlie\" Reed receives an invitation to a lavish weekend on a secluded island, she thinks it's the perfect opportunity to boost her fledgling detective agency. But when the enigmatic host turns up dead, it's clear this won't be the relaxing getaway anyone had in mind.</p> <p>With the storm cutting off communication and all escape routes, Charlie must navigate a house full of eccentric guests—all with dark secrets of their own. As tensions rise and accusations fly, it becomes a race against time to uncover the murderer before they strike again.</p> <p>Death by Invitation is a charming cozy mystery filled with intrigue, suspense, and unexpected twists. Perfect for fans of whodunits with a sprinkle of humor and a dash of danger.</p> <p>Listen now and sleuth the clues today!</p> <p>Special thanks to the members of Nellie H. Steele's Mystery Readers' group who were selected to appear as characters in this book!</p>"; 
